      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. specifically, i want to tackle the counter-argument that meritocracy is a better way to organize society. some people argue that wealth should only be based on individual talent and hard work. how can i frame that meritocracy argument as being basically incompatible with achieving racial equity? i want to show why that viewpoint is actually a barrier to justice.",
